Required Components to Develop Solutions
IDE/Simulation Software: Cisco Packet Tracer (preferably latest version with IoT support)
Hardware Components in Simulation:
Home Gateway (acts as a central controller)
Wireless Router or Access Point
Smart Fan (IoT device)
Smart Lamp (IoT device)
Motion Sensor or Temperature Sensor for automation triggers
Smartphone or End Device for remote monitoring and control
Programming/Configuration: Use Cisco Packet Tracer IoT programming blocks or scripting (e.g., JavaScript, Python, or Blockly within Packet Tracer)
